text: Somatidia latula is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Broun in 1893. It contains the varietas Somatidia latula var. obesula.BioLib.cz - Somatidia latula. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1893
title: Somatidia latula
